            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rewards-left-wrapper">
        <div class="rewards-inner">
          <img class="rewards-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0107/7431/5072/files/RR-reskin-loyalty_discounts_AST_sign_up_icon.svg?v=1658851662">
          <div class="rewards-inner-right">
            <h2 class="jc-h2-heading">Sign Up</h2>
            <p class="paragraph-text">Redeem your points for discounts on your CBD purchases! All you have to do is <a href="https://www.rrmeds.com/account/register" class="paragraph-link">create an account</a>. Plus, you'll get 100 points just for signing up.</p>
